can be used for manual address				calculations.The use of include or header files was avoided.R E A D   M E   	For XLR8SET, Copyright 1990, M. A. D. Software								007015								Page  2Copyright Information for all material on this disk   You may use the binary or source on any or all of your personal systems.If you sell a system(s), you may transfer the software to a single entityonly.  At the time of transfer, you must destroy all other copies you possess.   You may not redistribute, publish or place the source or binary where itcan be transferred by others.  Bulletin boards or other publicly-accessiblesystems may not offer this material in any form for download.  The materialson this disk are copyrighted works.   You may make any changes to the program that you need for your particularoperating environment.  You may not redistribute the binary or source, evenif you made changes to it.  You may provide the changes themselves in aform that can be applied to the unmodified source (or binary) by others.